# Ola Rides Analytics â€“ Streamlit App

This Streamlit application serves as the **presentation layer** for the
Ola Rides Analytics project.

It is designed for quick demos, walkthroughs, and non-technical stakeholders
to explore key insights without opening Power BI.



##  Purpose of the App

- Showcase key business metrics and insights
- Display SQL query outputs in tabular form
- Provide a lightweight interface for interacting with the analysis
- Complement Power BI dashboards for presentations and demos

This app intentionally avoids heavy business logic and focuses on clarity,
speed, and usability.



##  What the App Includes

- High-level KPIs (rides, revenue, ratings)
- Filtered views by vehicle type and day of week
- SQL-based summary tables
- Embedded Power BI screenshots for reference



## Tech Stack

- Python
- Streamlit
- Pandas
- SQL (pre-processed outputs)



